一个找到你想要寻找的目标的方法

161
00:10:22.744 --> 00:10:24.404
is to take out an ad.
就是发出一个广告。

162
00:10:24.428 --> 00:10:26.407
So let's read this one together.
我们一起来看看这一条。

163
00:10:26.431 --> 00:10:30.241
Wanted: country to pioneer carbon dividends plan.
诚需：碳红利计划的国家先驱。

164
00:10:30.265 --> 00:10:32.124
Cost to country: zero.
国家成本：零。

165
00:10:32.732 --> 00:10:35.011
Starting date: as soon as possible.
起始日期：即日可上岗。

166
00:10:34.885 --> 00:10:38.421
Advantages: most effective climate solution,
优势：最有效的气候策略，

167
00:10:38.501 --> 00:10:40.258
popular and populist,
认可度高，平民化，

168
00:10:40.282 --> 00:10:42.124
pro-growth and pro-business,
促进增长，促进商业化，

169
00:10:42.148 --> 00:10:45.490
shrinks government and helps the working class.
缩减政府机构，帮助劳动阶层。

170
00:10:47.101 --> 00:10:52.418
Additional compensation: gratitude of current and future generations,
额外补助：当代和子孙后代的无限感恩，

171
00:10:53.458 --> 00:10:55.626
including my daughter.
还包括我的女儿。

172
00:10:56.031 --> 00:10:57.183
Thank you.
谢谢大家。

173
